WAF.F5ASM.001: Server Unavailable Error


Description
This alert is activated when a web server exclusively provides responses categorized under the 5xx range, signaling server-side errors


KQL Query:

F5ASM
| where TimeGenerated >ago(20m)
| summarize count500=countif(ResponseCode between (500 ..599 )),count200=countif(ResponseCode !between (500..599)) by Host,bin(TimeGenerated,5m)
| summarize response_200=make_set(count200),response_500=make_set(count500),make_set(TimeGenerated) by Host
| extend full200sum=array_sum(response_200),full500sum=array_sum(response_500)
| where (full500sum-full200sum)>500
